title: Lan Ke Qi Yuan
summary: Leaves fell on the chess game by the side of Rotten Ke, and the old trees played against each other due to the uninteresting son of Tian Yuan, and then looked back on the vast mountains and seas… When he woke up, Ji Yuan became a half-blind beggar in a dilapidated mountain temple. The sword, the sacred stick and one mouth are the foundation for Ji Yuan to settle down in this terrible world.
